  "texts": [
    "Moreover, as sensing hardware becomes more capable and data-rich, there is a growing need for advanced AI models that can make sense of this complex, multimodal input.",
    "This shift emphasizes not only the accuracy of raw detection, but also the interpretability, synthesis, and personalization of sensory experiences.",
    "In this context, several frontier technologies are emerging to shape the next generation of AI-driven sensory systems.",
    "The next frontier of sensory modeling lies in multimodal AI architectures that integrate olfactory, gustatory, visual, and even haptic modalities into unified computational frameworks (Min et al. 2025).",
    "Rather than analyzing chemical features in isolation, these systems jointly interpret diverse sensory signals to construct holistic representations of flavor perception."
  ],
